tree = ete3.Tree('tests/tree_files/tree.nwk')
weights = {'2018-SEQ-1315.fasta': 2, '2018-SEQ-1271.fasta': 0.5}

branch = newtree.get_leaves_by_name('2018-SEQ-1271.fasta')
